Such was the peace made between them : the wall was immediately pulled down, and we were set at liberty. When we returned to the moon, our companions met and embraced m, shedding tears of joy, as did Endymion also. He intreated us to remain there, or to go along with the new colony, promifing to give me his son in marriage, for they have no women there; this 1 could by no means be persuaded το, but begged he would let us down into the sea. As he found I could not be prevailed on to stay, after feasting us most nobly for seven days, he dismissed us.
